  "description": "I opened up this babble and, as is becoming habit, gave it some name in the form of, \u0026ldquo;On some topic or another.\u0026rdquo; In this case, it was \u0026ldquo;On the emsean paracosm\u0026rdquo;\nLike that\u0026rsquo;s any sort of real thing, the emsean paracosm.\nWell, it is now that I\u0026rsquo;ve made that node, so I can link to it.\nBut it doesn\u0026rsquo;t have meaning until we give it some intension, and for that we need to do some conceptual analysis.\n",
